item.title: How would i fix this error
item.dc:creator: @3lv3n_snip3r 3lv3n snip3r
item.description:
@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

Is that arrow in the wrong spot? It’s point at the if instead of what’s in the if statement. If it’s referring to the c, add this in your class:

[code]private Client c;

public BankX2(Client Client) {
	this.c = Client;
}[/code]

And import your Client class.
If it’s referring to the inTrade, you would need to declare the variable.
